<%- include('partials/header') %>

<main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-3">
    <nav class="text-xs text-slate-500 mb-3 flex space-x-2">
        <a href="/" class="hover:underline">Home</a>
        <span>&gt;</span>
        <span class="text-slate-800 font-medium">Privacy Policy</span>
    </nav>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 p-8 md:p-12">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-slate-500 border-b border-slate-200 pb-6 mb-8">Last updated: June 14, 2026</p>

        <div class="space-y-8 text-slate-700">
            
            <section>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">1. Our Commitment to Privacy</h2>
                <p>School Sentiment is built on trust and anonymity. We collect minimal personal data by design. This policy explains what information we do collect and why.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="bg-green-50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-green-200">
                <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-green-800 mb-2">✅ What We DO NOT Collect</h2>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 text-green-700">
                    <li>Your name or real identity</li>
                    <li>Your physical address</li>
                    <li>Payment or credit card information</li>
                    <li>Your browsing history outside School Sentiment</li>
                    <li>Location data (unless you voluntarily use "Schools Near Me")</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">2. What Data We Collect</h2>
                
                <div class="mb-4">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">2.1 When You Write a Review (Anonymous)</h3>
                    <p>You can write reviews without creating an account. When you do, we collect:</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
                        <li><strong>Your review content</strong> (text, ratings, school name)</li>
                        <li><strong>Your IP address</strong> (to prevent spam and abuse)</li>
                        <li><strong>Browser type and device information</strong> (for analytics)</li>
                        <li><strong>Date and time of submission</strong></li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-500">This data is stored anonymously and is not linked to your identity.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="mb-4">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">2.2 When You Create an Account (Optional)</h3>
                    <p>If you choose to create an account using magic link login, we additionally collect:</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
                        <li><strong>Your email address</strong> (only to send magic links and manage your account)</li>
                        <li><strong>A list of reviews you have written</strong> (linked to your account, but still anonymous to others)</li>
                        <li><strong>Reviews you have saved/favourited</strong></li>
                        <li><strong>Ads you have posted</strong> on the School Noticeboard</li>
                        <li><strong>Ads you have saved</strong> for later viewing</li>
                        <li><strong>Schools you follow</strong> to receive notifications</li>
                        <li><strong>Messages you send and receive</strong> about ads</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-500">We never sell or share your email address with third parties.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="mb-4">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">2.3 School Staff Accounts & Verification</h3>
                    <p>If you are a school staff member claiming your school, we collect:</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
                        <li><strong>Your full name and work email address</strong></li>
                        <li><strong>Your role at the school</strong></li>
                        <li><strong>Work phone and website (optional)</strong></li>
                        <li><strong>School description (optional)</strong></li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-500">This information is used only to verify your association with the school and to display school contact information on the school profile page (with your consent).</p>
                </div>

                <div class="mb-4">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">2.4 When You Post on the Noticeboard</h3>
                    <p>When you post an ad on the School Noticeboard, we collect:</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
                        <li><strong>Item title, description, price, and condition</strong></li>
                        <li><strong>Photos you upload</strong> (up to 5 per ad)</li>
                        <li><strong>School name associated with the ad</strong></li>
                        <li><strong>Your email address</strong> (so buyers can contact you via the messaging system)</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-500">Your email address is never displayed publicly. Buyers contact you through our secure messaging system.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="mb-4">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">2.5 Notifications</h3>
                    <p>If you follow a school, we may send you:</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
                        <li><strong>Email notifications</strong> when new reviews or ads are posted at schools you follow</li>
                        <li><strong>In-app notifications</strong> (visible when you are logged in)</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-500">You can unfollow any school at any time to stop receiving notifications.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="mb-4">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">2.6 Cookies and Similar Technologies</h3>

                <div class="mt-4">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Cookies We Use</h3>
                    <div class="overflow-x-auto">
                        <table class="w-full text-sm border border-slate-200 rounded-lg">
                            <thead class="bg-slate-50">
                                <tr>
                                    <th class="text-left p-2 border-b">Cookie Name</th>
                                    <th class="text-left p-2 border-b">Purpose</th>
                                    <th class="text-left p-2 border-b">Duration</th>
                                    <th class="text-left p-2 border-b">Essential?</th>
                                </tr>
                            </thead>
                            <tbody>
                                <tr class="border-b">
                                    <td class="p-2 font-mono text-xs">sessionToken</td>
                                    <td class="p-2">Keeps you logged in to your account</td>
                                    <td class="p-2">30 days</td>
                                    <td class="p-2">Yes</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td class="p-2 font-mono text-xs">cookieConsent</td>
                                    <td class="p-2">Remembers your cookie preference</td>
                                    <td class="p-2">1 year</td>
                                    <td class="p-2">Yes (functional)</td>
                                </tr>
                            </tbody>
                        </table>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-2">We do not use any third-party tracking cookies, advertising cookies, or analytics cookies.</p>
                </div>                    <p>We use a single cookie only when you are logged in to keep you signed in. No tracking cookies, advertising cookies, or analytics cookies are used.</p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                    <li><strong>Display your reviews and ads</strong> - Publicly shown on school pages and noticeboard</li>
                    <li><strong>Enable messaging</strong> - Facilitate communication between buyers and sellers</li>
                    <li><strong>Send notifications</strong> - Email and in-app alerts for followed schools</li>
                    <li><strong>Prevent abuse</strong> - IP addresses help us block spam and fake reviews</li>
                    <li><strong>Improve our service</strong> - Anonymous analytics help us understand how people use the site</li>
                    <li><strong>Send magic links</strong> - If you have an account, we email you login links (no marketing emails)</li>
                    <li><strong>Verify school staff</strong> - Confirm eligibility to claim and reply to reviews</li>
                    <li><strong>Manage your saved items</strong> - Remember which reviews and ads you have saved</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">4. Data Retention</h2>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                    <li><strong>Reviews</strong> - Stored indefinitely (anonymously)</li>
                    <li><strong>Ads</strong> - Stored for 30 days after expiry, then deleted</li>
                    <li><strong>Photos</strong> - Stored as long as the ad exists</li>
                    <li><strong>Messages</strong> - Stored indefinitely (both parties can see history)</li>
                    <li><strong>IP addresses</strong> - Retained for 90 days, then anonymized</li>
                    <li><strong>Account data</strong> - Retained until you delete your account</li>
                    <li><strong>Magic link tokens</strong> - Deleted after 15 minutes or immediately after use</li>
                    <li><strong>School claim data</strong> - Retained for audit purposes</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">5. Your Rights (UK GDPR)</h2>
                <p>Under UK data protection law, you have the right to:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
                    <li><strong>Access</strong> - Request a copy of your data</li>
                    <li><strong>Rectification</strong> - Correct inaccurate data</li>
                    <li><strong>Erasure</strong> - Request deletion of your account and associated data</li>
                    <li><strong>Restrict processing</strong> - Limit how we use your data</li>
                    <li><strong>Data portability</strong> - Receive your data in a portable format</li>
                    <li><strong>Object</strong> - Object to certain data processing (including notifications)</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="mt-3">To exercise these rights, email us at <a href="mailto:privacy@schoolsentiment.co.uk" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline">privacy@schoolsentiment.co.uk</a></p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">6. Data Sharing</h2>
                <p>We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal data. We share data only in these limited circumstances:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
                    <li><strong>Legal requirements</strong> - If required by law enforcement or court order</li>
                    <li><strong>Service providers</strong> - Hosting and email providers (who also cannot use your data)</li>
                    <li><strong>With your consent</strong> - If you explicitly agree</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">7. Children's Privacy</h2>
                <p>School Sentiment is used by parents, students, and staff. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you are under 13, please use the site with a parent or guardian.</p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">8. Security</h2>
                <p>We implement reasonable security measures to protect your data, including encryption and secure HTTPS connections. However, no internet transmission is 100% secure.</p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
                <p>We may update this Privacy Policy occasionally. The latest version will always be posted here with the effective date at the top. Continued use of School Sentiment after changes means you accept the revised policy.</p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">10. Contact Us</h2>
                <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or your data, please contact:</p>
                <p class="mt-2"><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:privacy@schoolsentiment.co.uk" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline">privacy@schoolsentiment.co.uk</a></p>
            </section>

            <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 mt-8 text-sm text-slate-600 border border-slate-200">
                <p class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">📋 Summary for parents and students:</p>
                <p>School Sentiment is designed to protect your privacy. You can write reviews completely anonymously. If you create an account, we only use your email to send login links and notifications (if you follow schools). Your messages, saved items, and followed schools are private to your account. We never sell your data, show you ads, or track you across the web. Your trust is our priority.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
